snippet.title: CATACHRESIS: A WAY TOO SCARY GAME launch trailer
snippet.description:
This is the launch trailer for Catachresis, an browser-based adventure/horror/narrative game mashup.

You can play it here: http://heylookatmygames.com/catachresis
You can follow me on twitter here: http://www.twitter.com/ckunzelman

HUGE HUGE MASSIVE AMAZING THANKS to everyone who sent in videos that allowed me to make this trailer. I couldn't have done this without your emotional and material support and every moment you spent looking scared was a moment that I will cherish forever (until the black hole takes us into heat death.)

The music in the trailer is by Anatra aka Zareen Katherine Price who composed the soundtrack for the game. You can purchase it here: http://dakinilaughter.bandcamp.com/album/catachresis-ost/
